"Light to medium body with medium carbonation. This is basically the classic IPA in my book. While the 90 and 120 Minutes and countless other IPAs are intentionally overhopped, DFH 60 is straight and simple by comparison, yet still has enough complexities to amuse and be extremely enjoyable. Will always be one of my favorites, no problem at all finishing one of these off."
